      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition. The exterior has several visible scratches and a few small dents. The interior shows moderate wear, including some staining on the carpets and fading on the dashboard. Mechanically, the car runs but may require some upcoming maintenance.",
