    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver despite showing its age. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and some fading in the clear coat, while the interior shows typical wear on the upholstery and plastic surfaces. Mechanically, the car is sound and starts up without issue, though it may require some routine maintenance soon to keep it in peak operating condition. It is a solid, budget-friendly option for someone looking for dependable transportation without the price tag of a newer model.",
      "price": 24500.0,
